{"tid":1828444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一個無冒牌/假貨既「淘寶」，仲有咩吸引力？","createTime":"2020-01-17T23:41:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T22:59:34.000Z","uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dc92a47885b025be4feaf4d987b8c7d785c6bdc7","tid":1828444,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T23:41:12.000Z","msg":"貿易協議中有提到保護知識產權，規定中美雙方除了明確在網上電商平台的盜版、假冒問題，中方應該提供有效的執法程序，令到版權持有者能在網上採取有效、迅速的行動，以應對侵權問題。<br />\n<br />\n如果發現有侵權貨品在電商平台出售，中方應要求迅速下架，將版權持有人收到通知後，提出司法或行政投訴的期限延長至20個工作日，及確保下架的信息有效。"},{"pid":"9faf878180e917795a533f81c9a040dd74e7db21","tid":1828444,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T23:45:02.000Z","msg":"除左假貨淘寶仲有咩賣??"},{"pid":"9f9291016772cb3c53d5c53e0826aa8f9ec136df","tid":1828444,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9faf878180e917795a533f81c9a040dd74e7db21","tid":1828444,"uid":253016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T23:45:02.000Z","msg":"除左假貨淘寶仲有咩賣??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T23:46:36.000Z","msg":"我都想知。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似來俄羅斯野食賣。前幾年高登仔吹捧。"},{"pid":"50079b5b032d2e3ce07dfd18a8032a39515025f7","tid":1828444,"uid":193077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"平"},{"pid":"f7421d78d09ad2e4a113132eae67fe77cd86f3c2","tid":1828444,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T22:47:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cea3ac949bb6b94560e7a7f5bc3f23675b8f4e69","tid":1828444,"uid":56999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T22:50:48.000Z","msg":"係支那<br />\n<br />\n佢自己公司先係正版<br />\n<br />\n呢個條款<br />\n到時會將外國正版公司d野下架<br />\n<br />\n得返假貨"},{"pid":"af1da2ab33c22591b5997c54865f73ef2a6d3d14","tid":1828444,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cea3ac949bb6b94560e7a7f5bc3f23675b8f4e69","tid":1828444,"uid":56999,"like":0,"